00:42.792 --> 00:44.377
{\an1}- Señor Hueso,
you gotta help me.

00:44.461 --> 00:45.837
- Certainly.

00:45.920 --> 00:48.715
{\an3}I will begin by teaching you
how to leave. Bye-bye.

00:48.798 --> 00:50.091
